data.description: LOVELY ONE STORY 3BR/2BA HOME IN NORTH COLUMBUS. MINUTES FROM TOWN AND CAFB, THIS WONDERFUL HOME LOCATED JUST OFF RIDGE ROAD HAS MUCH TO OFFER- FRESH PAINT THROUGHOUT, SPACIOUS LIVING AREA W/GAS FIREPLACE , LG UPDATED & REMODELED KITCHEN W/SS APPLIANCES, DINING AREA, OFFICE PLUS A HEATED & COOLED SUNPORCH,  3-CAR CARPORT, WORKSHOP WITH ELECTRICITY & BUILT-IN SINK, PEGBOARDS FOR TOOLS,  RV PARKING WITH W/50 AMP OUTLET + RV DUMPSITE CONNECTED TO SEWER. HOME IS WIRED FOR A GENERATOR PLUS HAS A 20AMP PLUG IN CARPORT FOR CHARGING AN ELECTRICAL VEHICLE, GOURMET GAS GRILL, TONS OF STORAGE & LARGE BACKYARD WHICH BACKS UP TO WOODED AREA, LOVELY & SERENE SETTING.   A MUST SEE!!!
